#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:36
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Overview` page, click :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`Add "
"widget`."
msgstr ""
"בעמוד :guilabel:`סקירה כללית`, יש ללחוץ על :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`הוסף "
"ווידג'ט`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:37
msgid "Add a :guilabel:`Widget name` to easily identify it."
msgstr "יש להוסיף :guilabel:`שם ווידג'ט` כדי לזהות אותו בקלות."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:38
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`Add Hostnames`, enter a custom hostname "
"(e.g., *example.com* or *subdomain.example.com*), then click :guilabel:`Add` "
"twice."
msgstr ""
"יש ללחוץ על :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`הוסף שמות מארח`, להזין שם מארח מותאם "
