":guilabel:`הוסף` פעמיים."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:40
msgid "Select a :guilabel:`Widget Mode`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`מצב Widget` :בחר ב:guilabel:`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:42
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Managed` mode is **recommended**, as it allows Turnstile to "
"prompt visitors to confirm they are human when necessary."
msgstr ""
"מומלץ להשתמש במצב :guilabel:`מנוהל`, שכן הוא מאפשר ל-Turnstile לבקש ממבקרים "
"לאשר שהם בני אדם בעת הצורך."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:0
